export const tableOption = {
  dialogWidth: '100%',
  dialogHeight: '100%',
  dialogFullscreen: true,
  page:false,
  align:'center',
  indexLabel: '序号',
  border: true,
  index: true,
  editBtn:false,
  delBtn:false,
  addBtn:false,
  viewBtn:false,
  refreshBtn: false,
  filterBtn:false,
  menuWidth:'100',
  card:true,
  column:[
    {  label:"场所编号", prop:"dwbh",hide:true,},
    {  label:"场所名称", prop:"dwmc",overHidden:true,},
    {  label:"行业类型", prop:"hylx",type: 'tree',
      dicUrl: '/admin/dict/tree',
      dicMethod: 'get',
      expandLevel: 1,
      dicQuery: {type:'HYLX'},
    },
    {  label:"经营状态", prop:"placeState",type:'select',
      dicUrl: '/portal/dict/getDict/za_003/jzxt',
      dicMethod: 'get',
    },
    {  label:"行政区划", prop:"areaCode",type: 'tree', expandLevel: 1, overHidden:true,
      dicUrl: '/portal/area/areaData',
      dicMethod: 'get',
      dicQuery: {},
      props:{
        label: "name",
        value: 'code'
      }
    },
    {  label:"管辖单位", prop:"sspcs",
      dicUrl: '/portal/dict/getDict/06/jzxt',
      dicMethod: 'get',
      overHidden:true,
    },
    {  label:"经营地址", prop:"address", overHidden:true,},
    {  label:"来源系统", prop:"lyxtType",overHidden:true,},
  ]

}

    {  label:"行业类型", prop:"hylx",type: 'tree',

    {  label:"经营状态", prop:"placeState",type:'select',

    {  label:"行政区划", prop:"areaCode",type: 'tree', expandLevel: 1, overHidden:true,

}
